OOC: Yup its Speedbreaker.

BIC:
Speedbreaker frowned, he didnt like the threats, and really wanted to
blast this robot, but if he knew where Shockwave was, Megatron would
have Speedbreakers head for ruining this opertunity. "Ummm, sure" he
said, transforming, and burning a rip into the ground, tearing away
towards the Dark Avian.
